commit.message: Moves code that is marked with `.top` to the beginning of the file
Write to `stdout` when no output file is specified
Check for trailing whitespace on CI
Publish to Hackage via a GitHub action

Cabal: use build-tool-depends on top of build-depends

This ensure future compatibility with newer tooling
and nix-style cabal builds.

Merge pull request #9 from kirelagin/file-utf8

Always use UTF-8 to read and write files
